My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 6

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

The competition heads to Perth as best friends and world travellers, Chole and Kelly, serve up their global flavours. Will their taste for the finer things in life translate to high class cooking? Plus, one team will be going home.
